{"tid":426761,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[ps4] fifa18 pro club招人! ! 招後衛準備比賽","createTime":"2017-10-07T02:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T00:49:26.000Z","uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1777d651177eca67ce3ae33c9ef46bbe9d077ed","tid":426761,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"廢隊招後衛CARRY後防（平時少人可打中場）<br />\n<br />\n搵固定球員 打2場就轉隊周圍R波打就不了<br />\n<br />\n之後會報比賽<br />\n上屆VPL 銀杯8強隊<br />\n平日輕鬆玩<br />\n比賽前認真<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人仔國籍不可以係支那</strong><br />\n<strong>要求開咪 性格豁達 易溝通</strong><br />\n<br />\n通常夜晚10點後玩到1點到 (早訓既都冇所謂,講聲就OK)<br />\n同支那仔一樣玻璃心 唔輸得 輸2場就慘過死老豆既請另謀高就<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想入就留psn 或search telegram :chung191919"},{"pid":"e20ee806b77047eb352a724d293f03149b3b5237","tid":426761,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d8b5be6448d4b17d9b71c046ec9faf817e8827","tid":426761,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646e115b5ebdfe195ddc3bfb4668fdc764335e17","tid":426761,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ab2046d76a76b7c9897a0e2d65fdf98fa02c9e","tid":426761,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo